": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Moscow\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The measures will cover all kinds of abuse, not just political attacks.\", \"from\": 1644, \"to\": 1715, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The IOC gave no details of what kind of access to their accounts athletes would be expected to give it.\", \"from\": 1716, \"to\": 1819, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1720, \"end\": 1723, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 9.767351313544932e-20, \"text\": \"IOC\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Bach also said political developments in France and upcoming snap parliamentary elections only weeks before the Olympics would not derail either preparations or the Games themselves.\", \"from\": 1821, \"to\": 2003, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1821, \"end\": 1825, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Johann_Sebastian_Bach\", \"score\": 0.9999999985786872, \"rank\": 1.421266867240922e-09, \"text\": \"Bach\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Johann_Sebastian_Bach\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Johann_Sebastian_Bach\"}, {\"begin\": 1862, \"end\": 1868, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.9326656387466984, \"rank\": 0.05702901827105679, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"No, we are not concerned,\\\" Bach said.\", \"from\": 2005, \"to\": 2043, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2033, \"end\": 2037, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Johann_Sebastian_Bach\", \"score\": 0.9999999985786872, \"rank\": 1.421266867240922e-09, \"text\": \"Bach\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], 